categories: Category:Jedi Masters of the Jedi Order

nodes.text: Luquena was a Jedi Master who served the Jedi Order and the Galactic Republic during the Cold War against the reconstituted Sith Empire. Luquena, Kirbi, Tre Trimbal, and another Jedi attempted to investigate a rakghoul warren on Taris, but they were killed by nekghouls.
